## Government Tender Announcement
### Contract Award for Marine Animal Response Services

The Department of Fisheries and Oceans (DFO) is seeking to award a contract to a pre-qualified supplier for the project titled "Supporting Response to Dead and Distressed Marine Animals in Maritimes Provinces."

#### Project Background

The project aims to provide support for the operation of a toll-free bilingual reporting call centre, coordination of marine animal response efforts, and response to marine animal incidents. The project also involves the provision of response guidance to authorized partners and the collection of basic marine animal incident data.

#### Key Project Objectives

* Ensure efficient reporting of incidents involving dead and distressed marine animals in the Maritimes Provinces
* Promote efficiency by reporting to a single hotline
* Support efforts to report incidents involving species listed under the Species at Risk Act (SARA)

#### Contract Award Details

* Tender Reference Number: cb-428-15885189
* Solicitation Number: 30004744
* Publication Date: 2023-09-29
* Tender Closing Date: 2023-10-23T14:00:00 (Expired)

#### Contract Specification

* The contract is awarded based on a pre-identified supplier
* The successful supplier will provide support services for the operation of a toll-free bilingual reporting call centre and coordination of marine animal response efforts
* The contract is expected to be completed in a single province: Prince Edward Island, Nova Scotia, New Brunswick, and Newfoundland and Labrador

#### Contact Information

* Name: Dina Al-Eryani
* Email: [Dina.Al-Eryani@dfo-mpo.gc.ca](mailto:Dina.Al-Eryani@dfo-mpo.gc.ca)
* Phone: (506) 282-2340
* Address: 200 Kent St, Ottawa, Ontario K1A 0E6, Canada

#### Tender Documents

* The tender notice and contract documents can be downloaded from the Canadabuys website at: [https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/21086/30004744---acan.pdf](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/21086/30004744---pac_2.pdf) (French version)
